  "title": "Microsoft Foundry, M365, and A365 - Our Agents Grow Up",
  "locked": false,
  "description": "Show how the invoice-review agent moves from a local proof of concept into an enterprise-ready deployment with data connections, hosting, Teams access, and governance.",
