      "time": "~20s",
      "narrative": "The local proof of concept showed that the task works. Now the agent needs to grow up. We move into an environment that gives Pharma Company the security, governance, and visibility required for production use.",
      "demo_actions": "Transition from the local POC to VS Code or the enterprise build environment. Frame this as the move from experiment to production.",
