      "time": "~35s",
      "narrative": "In VS Code, we connect the agent to the right IQs and make the data access explicit. The POC used simulated records. This version can reach real enterprise evidence, with visible guardrails around what tools the agent can call and when.",
      "demo_actions": "Open the agent project in VS Code. Show configuration for IQs, tool access, or policy controls. Point to the guardrails on tool calls.",
