      },
      "time": "~35s",
      "narrative": "That matters because invoice assurance depends on more than the invoice itself. The agent now has the right toolbox to pull contracts, invoice records, receipts, batch records, quality status, milestone approvals, materials data, and capacity context into one review.",
      "demo_actions": "Open the toolbox or connected data sources. Walk through the evidence sources the agent can access.",
