        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~30s",
      "narrative": "Once connected, we deploy the agent as a hosted agent in Foundry. This gives us a managed runtime with isolation and a clear execution path we can inspect.",
      "demo_actions": "Deploy the agent in Foundry. Show hosted agent setup, cloud isolation cues, and a simple execution.",
